## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="24500-102">Windows 바탕 화면 음성의 컬렉션으로 인식된 구 반환 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedWordUnit> 또는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.ReplacementText> 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24500-102">Windows Desktop Speech returns recognized phrases as collections of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedWordUnit> or <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.ReplacementText> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24500-103">각 개체는 단일 단어 또는 문장 부호에 해당합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24500-103">Each object corresponds to a single word or punctuation mark.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24500-104">`DisplayAttributes` 속성은 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedWordUnit> 또는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.ReplacementText> 의 멤버를 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DisplayAttributes> 방법을 인쇄 여백에 설명 하는 열거형은 특정된 단어 또는 문장 부호 주위의 처리 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24500-104">The `DisplayAttributes` property of a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedWordUnit> or <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.ReplacementText> uses a member of the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DisplayAttributes> enumeration to describe how print spacing is handled around a given word or punctuation mark.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="24500-105">두 개 이상의 멤버는 `DisplayAttributes` 열거형을 비트 단위 여 결합할 수 있습니다 `OR` 특정 단어를 표시 하는 방법을 지정할 수 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24500-105">Two or more members of the `DisplayAttributes` enumeration may be combined by a bit-wise `OR` to specify how a particular word should be displayed.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="24500-106">표시 형식을 사용 하 여 음성 인식기는 특정 언어입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24500-106">The display formatting that the speech recognizer uses is language specific.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="24500-107">예를 들어 기본 시스템 문법에서 제공을 사용 하 여 인식 엔진에 입력된 구 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DictationGrammar> 은 "Hello 쉼표 기간 있다고"입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24500-107">For example, suppose the input phrase to a recognition engine using the default system grammar provided by <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DictationGrammar> is "Hello comma he said period".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="24500-108">인식 엔진을 반환 합니다는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase> 5 개 포함 된 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedWordUnit> 다음을 포함 하는 개체를 다음으로 문자열 `DisplayAttributes` 값입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24500-108">Then the recognition engine returns a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase> containing five <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedWordUnit> objects containing the following strings with the following `DisplayAttributes` values.</span></span>  
  
|<span data-ttu-id="24500-109">항목</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24500-109">Item</span></span>|`DisplayAttributes`|  
|----------|-------------------------|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24500-110">Hello</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24500-110">Hello</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24500-111">OneTrailingSpace</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24500-111">OneTrailingSpace</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24500-112">,</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24500-112">,</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24500-113">OneTrailingSpace &#124; ConsumeLeadingSpaces</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24500-113">OneTrailingSpace &#124; ConsumeLeadingSpaces</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24500-114">he</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24500-114">he</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24500-115">OneTrailingSpace</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24500-115">OneTrailingSpace</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24500-116">말합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24500-116">said</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24500-117">OneTrailingSpace</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24500-117">OneTrailingSpace</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="24500-118">이어야 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24500-118">.</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="24500-119">OneTrailingSpace &#124; ConsumeLeadingSpaces</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24500-119">OneTrailingSpace &#124; ConsumeLeadingSpaces</span></span>|  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="24500-120">이 인식된 된 구와를 인쇄에 대해 반환 되는 텍스트: "Hello, 있다고 합니다."</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24500-120">The text returned for this recognized phrase is printed as: "Hello, he said."</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="24500-121">사용 하 여 다음 예제는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedWordUnit.DisplayAttributes%2A> 속성 목록으로 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedWordUnit> 단어 구의으로 형식을 지정할 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24500-121">The following example uses the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedWordUnit.DisplayAttributes%2A> property of a list of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedWordUnit> objects to format the words as a phrase.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
  
// Use the DisplayAttributes property to format speech as text.   
  
static string GetDisplayText(List<RecognizedWordUnit> words)  
{  
  StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();  
  
  // Concatenate the word units together. Use the DisplayAttributes  
  // property of each word unit to add or remove white space around  
  // the word unit.  
  foreach (RecognizedWordUnit word in words)  
  {  
    if ((word.DisplayAttributes  
      & DisplayAttributes.ConsumeLeadingSpaces) != 0))  
    {  
      sb = new StringBuilder(sb.ToString().TrimEnd());  
    }  
  
    sb.Append(word.Text);  
  
    if ((word.DisplayAttributes  
      & DisplayAttributes.OneTrailingSpace) != 0)  
    {  
      sb.Append(" ");  
    }  
    else if ((word.DisplayAttributes  
      & DisplayAttributes.TwoTrailingSpaces) != 0)  
    {  
      sb.Append("  ");  
    }  
  }  
  
  return sb.ToString();  
}  
  
```
